      <notesStmt>
        <note>Title from colophon.</note>
        <note>The text matches the initial portions of UPenn Indic Ms. Item 1434 and Item 1380, with variant readings. See also Items 597, Item 2858, etc.</note>
        <note>Written 10 lines per leaf.</note>
        <note>Good condition. Mistakes covered over with yellow.</note>
        <note>Begins, f. 1r: śrī om̐ ādhāraśaktyai namaḥ kūrmāsanāya namaḥ yogāsanāya namaḥ anaṁtāsanāya namaḥ vimalāsanāya namaḥ madhye paramasukhāsanāya namaḥ ūrdhvakeśi virūpākṣi māṁsaśroṇitabhojane tiṣṭha devi śikhāmadhye cāmuṁḍe hy aparājite iti śikhābaṁdhanaṁ</note>
        <note>Text ends, f. 3r: vam ity amṛtabījena ṣoḍaśa vā raṁ amṛtīkṛtya vaṁ 26</note>
        <note>Colophon, f. 3r: iti bhūśuddhiḥ śrīgajānanārpaṇam astu</note>
